Before we get into assessment best practices, let’s talk about how to tell ChatGPT what you want
Simple exercise showing the difference in responses after refining prompt. Learner enters these just to see how responses differ. 

<i>Possible examples:</i>

- <b>Prompt 1:</b> “What should I have for dinner?”
- <b>Prompt 2:</b> “what should I have for dinner if I want a unique dining experience in San Francisco, CA 
- <b>Prompt 3:</b> “what should I have for dinner if I want a unique dining experience in San Francisco, CA, and I'm vegetarian, and I'm on a budget”

